dc_title_s: Status of Free and Open Public Geospatial Data from Counties: Minnesota
dc_description_s: This map shows the free and open data status of county public geospatial (GIS) data across Minnesota. The accompanying data set can be used to make similar maps using GIS software.  To see if a county's data is distributed via the Minnesota Geospatial Commons, check the Commons organizations page:  https://gisdata.mn.gov/organization  To see if a county distributes data via its website, check the link(s) on the Minnesota County GIS Contacts webpage:  http://www.mngeo.state.mn.us/county_contacts.html
